## Asset Lifecycle

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Procurement
    Procurement --> Receiving
    Receiving --> Commissioning
    Commissioning --> ActiveUse
    ActiveUse --> Maintenance
    ActiveUse --> Transfer
    ActiveUse --> Allocation
    Transfer --> ActiveUse
    Allocation --> ActiveUse
    Maintenance --> ActiveUse
    ActiveUse --> Disposal
    Disposal --> [*]
```
